text.section:
The filing of a financing statement is not necessary to perfect a security interest:
That is perfected under KRS 355.9-308(4), (5), (6), or (7);
That is perfected under KRS 355.9-309 when it attaches;
In property subject to a statute, regulation, or treaty described in KRS 355.9-311(1);
In goods in possession of a bailee which is perfected under KRS 355.9-312(4)(a) or (b);
In certificated securities, documents, goods, or instruments which is perfected without filing, control, or possession under KRS 355.9-312(5), (6), or (7);
In collateral in the secured party's possession under KRS 355.9-313;
In a certificated security which is perfected by delivery of the security certificate to the secured party under KRS 355.9-313;
In deposit accounts, electronic chattel paper, electronic documents, investment property, or letter-of-credit rights which is perfected by control under KRS 355.9-314;
In proceeds which is perfected under KRS 355.9-315; or
That is perfected under KRS 355.9-316.
